author: @AsianS9ake
text: Introduction To Flask Web Framework Key Concepts Flask is a popular web framework in Python used for developing web applications, web APIs, and machine learning applications.  WSGI (Web Server Gateway Interface) is a crucial protocol for hosting web applications on web servers.  Jinja2 is a templating engine used in Flask for creating dynamic web pages.  Feedback loops are effective in promoting completion and improvement in the development process.  The integration of web templates with data sources like ML models and databases is essential in creating practical applications.
